refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Ds\SeqDs\Seq::merge mixedvalues
Returns the result of adding all given values to the seq.

&reftitle.parameters;


  values



      A traversable object or an &array;.

&reftitle.returnvalues;
The result of adding all given values to the seq, effectively the same as adding the values to a copy, then returning that copy.
The current instance won't be affected.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Ds\Seq::merge example


<?php
$seq = new \Ds\Seq([1, 2, 3]);

var_dump($seq->merge([4, 5, 6]));
var_dump($seq);
?>


